      1          /**
      2           *  @file
      3           *
      4           *  @brief      Module that stores references and definitions to the meaningful variables on the platform.
      5           *
      6           *  @details    This is a hub module from where you can access variables using an index. To make it happen you need to configure the PRV file with
      7           *  			the proper data: It's necessary to declare extern variables that you'll add to DATA_HOLDER_INITIALIZE. On this constant, you add the elements
      8           *  			using DATATYPE_TYPE as reference. Fill up all fields.
      9           *  			Important: this module manages 8 and 16 bits variables and Regulations using the VARIABLE_REGULATION_HUB position and the Regulation module.
     10           *
     11           *  @copyright  Copyright 2015-2016 Whirlpool Corporation. All rights reserved - CONFIDENTIAL
